ğŸŸ¢ Solution 1: Track progressive time, not jumps (MOST IMPORTANT)
Backend logic
MAX_INCREMENT = 15 # seconds per heartbeat

delta = current_time - progress.last_watched_second

if delta > 0 && delta <= MAX_INCREMENT
  progress.last_watched_second = current_time
end


What this does:

Allows natural forward playback

Rejects large jumps

